ActCanada Pension Plan Investment Board Act
PrecisAppointment of DOUGLAS W. MAHAFFY of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canada Pension Plan Investment Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years, effective October 27, 2009, in the place of Helen K. Sinclair.
